	<Folder id="0EFC1A57A43F955C2143">
		<name>Conservation - trails + habitat</name>
		<visibility>0</visibility>
		<snippet></snippet>
		<description><![CDATA[<div>Existing or subdivided parcels stewarded in combination between Kendell, Kestral, Trustees, and MA Audabon.&nbsp;<br></div><div><br></div><div>- Multi-use trails allow recreational access for Hampshire housing residents, Indigenous groups, and educational programs from Hitchcock.&nbsp;<br></div><div><br></div><div>Boundaries drawn based on wetland protection, habitat continuity between parcels, and walking trail potential in anticipation of mindful housing and mixed use development<br></div><div><br></div>]]></description>
		<styleUrl>#__managed_style_572793F58B401C68135C</styleUrl>
